g(x,y,\lambda)=x^2y-\lambda (x+y-3)
\partial _y g=0\iff x^2-\lambda=0\iff x=\pm \sqrt{\lambda}
\partial _x g=0\iff 2xy-\lambda=0\iff xy=\frac{\lambda}2\iff y=\pm \frac{\sqrt{\lambda}}2
\partial _{\lambda} g=0\iff x+y=3
